grml-etc (1.0.10) unstable; urgency=low

  [Michael Prokop]
  * /etc/init.d/grml-reboot:
    - use default of 2 minutes timeout for "Please remove CD" (merge
      with Knoppix)
    - unmount nfs4 and smbfs as well in nfs code, use -l option instead
      of -r
    - do not rmmod all (unused) kernel modules anymore
    - try to unmount all remaining filesystems manually

  [Andreas Gredler]
  * /et/wvdial.conf.umts: added support for t-mobile usb cards and boxes

