grml-etc (0.7-38) unstable; urgency=low

  * /etc/skel/.zshrc
    - updated function wikide as requested by Matthias Kopfermann.
    - added function exirename to rename jpg files based on their
      exif header using jhead
    - check whether compinit is already available before loading
      it, otherwise our own completion does not work anymore
  * /etc/runlevel.conf*: updated for /etc/init.d/bootlocal* stuff.
    /etc/runlevel.conf.livecd has been adapted to current
    /var/lib/dpkg/info/initscripts.postinst version.
  * /etc/zsh/zshenv: set PATH only if $PATH is empty or is "/bin:/usr/bin".

 -- Michael Prokop <mika@grml.org>  Sun,  4 Jun 2006 15:07:16 +0200

