  * /etc/zsh/zshrc: use '-la' instead of '-lA' in la alias.
    Too confusing for human brains, sorry Matthias. :)

 -- Michael Prokop <mika@grml.org>  Tue, 30 May 2006 00:10:05 +0200

grml-etc (0.7-36) unstable; urgency=low

  * /etc/skel/.zshrc: support /.zshrc.global.
