grml-etc (0.6-9) unstable; urgency=low

  * Don't check for set $HISTFILE, $HISTSIZE and $SAVEHIST - just
    set it. Otherwise zsh history does not work as expected.
  * Changed 'checkBootParam' in /etc/init.d/grml-reboot to simple
    grep command so we don't depend on grml-shlib currently.
  * Updated /etc/skel/.fluxbox/keys, added some key bindings.

 -- Michael Prokop <mika@grml.org>  Sat, 18 Feb 2006 17:48:10 +0100

