grml-etc (0.2-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Updated /etc/zsh/zshrc and /etc/zsh/zshenv.
  * Fixed symlink /etc/skel/.irssi/scripts/autorun/scriptassist.pl
    which points now to /usr/share/irssi/scripts/scriptassist.pl
    instead of /GRML/..... [thanks, Jimmy!]
  * Fixed /etc/skel/.terminfo/mostlike-stuff (changed 'smul=\E[32m'
    to 'smul=\E[1;32m') [thanks, Matthias!]

 -- Michael Prokop <mika@grml.org>  Thu, 27 Jan 2005 16:12:33 +0100

